formula: eta(z)*eta(14z)^11/(eta(2z)^5*eta(7z)^7)Euler transform of period 14 sequence [ -1, 4, -1, 4, -1, 4, 6, 4, -1, 4, -1, 4, -1, 0, ...]. - _Michael Somos_, Nov 10 2005
